{"tid":1597514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港人治港 高度自治","createTime":"2019-09-27T03:33:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T06:22:52.000Z","uid":8891,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"db497a8ee8896aff42543bebc293e13bc1997d9d","tid":1597514,"uid":8891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:33:31.000Z","msg":"80年代中英兩方已經明白香港要維持實力，必須要高度自治，國際多國亦多次支持香港自治，我們的盟友美國多次強調中共影響香港自治。<br />\n<br />\n國際開左張好牌，香港人要識做，新口號要有自治、新文宣要向自己人推廣香港自治重要性。<br />\n<br />\n如果要為今次革命加一句自治新口號，我推介「港人治港，高度自治」，原因係香港人由細聽到大，簡單易明。"},{"pid":"7445af8f7862d33d79c65b2b8c9256223e504dae","tid":1597514,"uid":71428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:35:44.000Z","msg":"唔要高度, 政府同中共一直用緊高度黎玩語言偽術"},{"pid":"d9bf0e47b95aaabd1ae884efddae2055ff07a9df","tid":1597514,"uid":290176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:44:00.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"5c7569962b2a3960880cae5e50c855672807c2dc","tid":1597514,"uid":8891,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7445af8f7862d33d79c65b2b8c9256223e504dae","tid":1597514,"uid":71428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:35:44.000Z","msg":"唔要高度, 政府同中共一直用緊高度黎玩語言偽術"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:49:52.000Z","msg":"小改：港人治港 香港自治<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29d692fbd7203696f79db0e464671603bc4309c7","tid":1597514,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:50:42.000Z","msg":"大家好， 我係連儂之路既搞手之一， 希望當日可以招募義工係集合點度幫手， 義工主要負責：<br />\n<br />\n1. 派發已經預先準備的文宣及工具<br />\n2. 指示貼牆人鏈方向<br />\n3. 幫助貼牆時有需要既手足<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既手足可以加入義工組：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/JuUURVkFBMmibh5vA_acGQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJuUURVkFBMmibh5vA_acGQ&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYgESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=05b89f24\" data-au